{"tid":1373983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線同後援 都請入一入黎30秒","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:58.000Z","uid":44034,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0c4e64ae1b82a2a06093d80e81509fcea133de","tid":1373983,"uid":44034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">俾30秒我多謝你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第一次發夢（ 一個人發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n行個陣<br />\nOn99上左石搏落唔番有絲打扶我跳番落黎<br />\n有前線關心我做乜著拖鞋咁勇<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n走個陣<br />\n有人問我要唔要衫換 <br />\n有人提醒我邊個出口有狗要小心<br />\n去到元朗西鐵有前線頂住俾時間我走<br />\n <br />\n無論前線定後援 第一次覺得<br />\n香港人 咁可愛 咁溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOn99聽到前面人嗌7點半走就幫手嗌<br />\n最後自己都留到10點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次會冷靜評估先<br />\n對唔住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝你地付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 急救科醫護  想問下之後除左發夢同airdrop地圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有乜野可以實際行動可以發揮所長 更有效支援到運動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6075629343a58cdcb589ee5cb7f129662d97350a","tid":1373983,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"溝通問題成為每一次打機嘅問大問題，到底點先可以令前排坦克同後排輔助可以溝通到呢？<br />\n<br />\n諗咗陣，發覺可以用顏色旗黎做訊號<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">前進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-larg